{"tid":1888963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超指登上包機106名港人中，88人持特區護照，18人持其他國家護照","createTime":"2020-02-20T13:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:06:53.000Z","uid":133680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf1c52a67fcfa90f7e7d47d3f5d9c235d3c517a","tid":1888963,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3861920340515226/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3861920340515226%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=a8412107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3861920340515226/</a><br />\n保安局局長 #李家超 表示，成功安排首批「#鑽石公主號」郵輪港人上包機，凌晨出發，今早抵港。所有人士送往火炭駿洋邨檢疫中心作14日檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，登上包機的乘客包括106名港人，當中88人持香港特區護照，18人持其他國家護照，所有人通過檢測及屬陰性，獲得日本厚生勞動省陰性名單。<br />\n<br />\n【李家超冀今日將所有檢測陰性港人接回】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3bRmBsO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bRmBsO&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=f888acde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3bRmBsO</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n【新聞專題﹕武漢肺炎】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3ay4mI2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ay4mI2&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=7fc7012a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3ay4mI2</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #即時新聞 #武漢肺炎 #包機"},{"pid":"b70ea0f353cc4797d97978d2b65bb94c1d31dc0f","tid":1888963,"uid":14494,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.renminbao.com/rmb/article_images/2013-3-30-130330fs01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.renminbao.com%2Frmb%2Farticle_images%2F2013-3-30-130330fs01.jpg&h=3f8a7843&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12e21f3813816bea4a0fd82d351a125d51da6cfd","tid":1888963,"uid":133680,"like":0,"disli